flowchart LR
    A[Lead submits form] --> B[Phone Validation API]
    B --> C[AI Urgency Scoring]
    C --> D{Score >= threshold?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Log to CRM<br/>Priority: High]
    D -- No --> F[Log to CRM<br/>Priority: Standard]
    E --> G{Phone valid?}
    G -- Yes --> H[SMS Alert]
    G -- No --> I[No SMS<br/>lead still logged]
